{"tid":550951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老表示：而家啲後生打佢就告你虐兒，好難教。","createTime":"2018-02-05T08:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T14:29:57.000Z","uid":169392,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a3aca067de44ff44ccce0412be4a8756011c12ae","tid":550951,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:33:25.000Z","msg":"放lunch 去咗廢老集中營m記買個包食，<br />\n等拎走時聽到後面兩個廢老討論現時啲細路好難教。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ＝廢老1<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ＝廢老2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咪話我話丫，而家啲細路好難教，一郁手就告你虐兒。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唉～以前係細路哥怕大人，而家係大人怕啲細路哥。搞到好易學壞<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇廢老郁手但唔覺自己係虐緊兒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家嘅細路係咪又比以前嘅細路壞？"},{"pid":"b84a8d83346d505dfca659542bc98cc4bae3fefb","tid":550951,"uid":605,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾唔識教咪打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ab6180743c2c240d8a5a11eecbb4753dc1b505","tid":550951,"uid":53421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"我細個唔聽話比阿媽拎牛肉刀斬tim ar"},{"pid":"b63512fcc9cc0242683bebe14f596079483aeac3","tid":550951,"uid":30495,"like":15,"dislike":13,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"認真 我覺得打係應該 <br />\n我由細到大都好頑皮 百厭 好彩因父母嘅嚴厲教導<br />\n到中學時期先無咁反叛學壞唔識諗後果<br />\n次次係街見到小朋友周圍跑又撞又唔識say sor<br />\n我次次心諗都同一句 點解咁撚無家教<br />\n<br />\n利申 90後 前期果段"},{"pid":"6c3bdaa6cd3ff5caa426ddd02c47b9d4f92452ef","tid":550951,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我細個唔聽話比阿媽拎牛肉刀斬tim ar</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你避到幾多刀？"},{"pid":"4601a32112e70cbb5bc949479214